data.description: Minutes from Madison, get away to the country in this move-in- ready single-story home on a large, fenced lot.  Range/oven, microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, blinds, gutters, ceiling fans, gas log fireplace, no carpet. Covered patio, privacy fence with double & single gates, large lot, with no neighbors behind. Gigabit fiber service, No HOA. Low county taxes.  Eligible for No Down Payment! Call to see today!
